  "dc:description": "Dataset containing mineral composition, speleothem formation types, and environmental measurements for 150 rock samples collected in the Postojna Cave System (Slovenia) between March and July 2024. Includes GPS coordinates, temperature, humidity, and XRD mineral identification.",

